{
  "1733110": {
    "name": "生灵沃野",
    "steam_appid": 1733110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/4b9552a12af39b69ae9e0ff944ed8327.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/4b9552a12af39b69ae9e0ff944ed8327.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/4b9552a12af39b69ae9e0ff944ed8327.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受委托担任领导者的角色，前往王国偏远的未知角落建立新的定居点。在那些被人遗忘之地，大自然荒蛮狂野，传说比想象中更加真实生动。在这个世界上体验不同季节和气候带来的挑战，这里的每一种动植物都在努力生存，同时领导你的村民。你愿意与大自然分享多少？你是否会努力争取平衡，还是会强制灭绝某些动物？沿着旧路走……或者找到自己的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻求或无视平衡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人类与自然界共享相同的空间和资源，相互影响。</strong>虽然在一开始的时候，人类的影响微不足道，但随着城市及其需求的增长，其影响力与日俱增。某些动物或群体有可能会灭绝或爆炸性繁殖，这取决于你的行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/2f210cf91edb0e521d323b7cf6c3977d.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/2f210cf91edb0e521d323b7cf6c3977d.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/2f210cf91edb0e521d323b7cf6c3977d.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立你的经济</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理资源的获取、提炼和分配。</strong>货物必须由具备时间和物品空间的人运送到所需地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/a6bd87b6abd606d3acb78f5faf84a2be.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/a6bd87b6abd606d3acb78f5faf84a2be.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/a6bd87b6abd606d3acb78f5faf84a2be.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关爱所有生物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理居民的需求。</strong>他们拥有“生命”，有特定的住所、工作场所以及各种各样的需求和目标。但动物也会吃喝睡觉、形成群体、寻求社交，并尝试找到自己在自然界的位置。即使是植物也需要水和合适的温度才能生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/d908176c2a8cd560207c9761a56cdb06.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/d908176c2a8cd560207c9761a56cdb06.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/d908176c2a8cd560207c9761a56cdb06.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >观察生机盎然的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>季节和天气会影响游戏玩法。</strong>某些植物只在特定的季节生长，炎热时需要更多的水，或者寒冷时期会冻结。人类和动物在冬天需要更多的能量来保持温暖，或在夏天需要更多的水来保持凉爽。在极端情况下，他们会精疲力竭，甚至可能受到伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/68f7307a27312134d6f7da883bdc14a9.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/68f7307a27312134d6f7da883bdc14a9.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/68f7307a27312134d6f7da883bdc14a9.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由掌控游戏节奏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>按照你的步调游玩。</strong>随时暂停游戏、加快或放慢速度。自然界的平衡是稳定的，随着游戏的发展，你的村民会产生更复杂的需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/c8890c2a94818557d254112bfd702789.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/c8890c2a94818557d254112bfd702789.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/c8890c2a94818557d254112bfd702789.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建你自己的场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在编辑器中创建你自己的地图和场景。</strong>你可以改变景观，生成植物和放置动物。你还可以连接水道，为旅行者创造新的路径。添加新的地图或将现有的地图连接起来，形成一个新的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/21605782f6dbe5878bc891227de6a64b.poster.avif?t=1765810812\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/21605782f6dbe5878bc891227de6a64b.webm?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733110/extras/21605782f6dbe5878bc891227de6a64b.mp4?t=1765810812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款建造策略游戏中体验对大自然独特的深度模拟，以及人类与自然之间复杂的相互依存关系。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同气候条件下的多个地图上同时管理资源的获取、提炼和分配。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理居民的需求。他们拥有“生命”，有特定的住所、工作场所以及独特的需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物会吃喝睡觉，并形成社会群体以尝试找到自己在自然界的位置。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >植物会生长，并受到人类和动物的行为及其环境的影响。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >季节和气候会影响游戏玩法，因为某些植物只在特定条件下生长。温度会影响人类、动物、植物和环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些派系与你采用相同的规则进行生产，你可以与其进行互动和贸易。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在编辑器中创建自己的地图和场景，并使用模组扩展它们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷人而平静的低多边形画风。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 日语, 韩语, 俄语, 波兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
